==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From the same as [[ἀριστον]] {{GG|712}} and [[ἄρχω]] {{GG|757}}; 
best ruling; 

===Pronunciation===
*Ἀρίσταρχος / Aristarchos / ar-is'-tar-khos

===Proper noun===
'''Ἀρίσταρχος'''

# Aristarchus, a Macedonian: - Aristarchus.

